  <main style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; justify-content: left;">
      <h2>Welcome to Curious</h2>
    <p>
      Curious is a digital interpretation system specifically designed for zoos and aquariums. Our innovative platform empowers your visitors to discover detailed information about animals in your exhibits using their own smartphones by scanning QR codes or tapping NFC tags. It's simple to set up, easy to use, and low-cost.
    </p>
    <br>

    <!-- <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/YOUR_VIDEO_ID" width="100%" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe> -->

    <h2>How Does It Work?</h2>
    <p>
      Curious bridges the gap between curiosity and knowledge. Visitors scan a QR code at an exhibit to unlock a treasure trove of information.
      <br>
      <br>
      Each page provides:
      <br>
      <br>
    </p>
    <ul class="benefit-list">
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>Detailed species profiles that include images and scientific data</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>Fascinating fun facts, up-to-date conservation status, and rich images.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>Optional audio-only mode to create a quick and easy audio guide for your site.</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- <p>[PLACEHOLDER FOR VIDEO]</p>     -->
    <br>

    <h2>Why Choose Curious?</h2>
    <ul class="benefit-list">
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Easy Setup Process:</strong>&nbsp;easily add your species and animals, along with some key information.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Seamless Integration:</strong>&nbsp;works on any smartphone or tablet, with no app downloads required.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Brand Customisation:</strong>&nbsp;hone the visitor experience with your own branding and tone of voice.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Eco-Friendly:</strong>&nbsp;improve your sustainability credentials by reducing reliance on signage and guidebooks.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Engaging Content:</strong>&nbsp;offer rich species profiles with images, videos, audio, and conservation data.</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Data-Driven Insights:</strong>&nbsp;understand your exhibit impact with detailed analytics on engagement and page views.</li>
    </ul>
    <br>

    <!-- <br> -->

    <h2>Experience Curious</h2>
    <p>
      Our sample test site is a great way to see how it all works. Use your phone to scan the QR code below, and explore our sample "Ocean Tank" exhibit. Dive into the species profiles and learn more about the animals within the tank.
    </p>
    <p>
      Scan the QR codes below with your mobile device - if you're already on a mobile device, just long press the image!
